  "instructions": [
    "Combine water, sesame oil, rice vinegar, honey, gochujang, and low-sodium soy sauce in a mason jar.",
    "Add pitted black olives, mashed gangwon-do garlic, and Korean chili flakes to the jar.",
    "Close the lid and place the jar in a pressure cooker.",
    "Pressure cook on high for 10 minutes.",
    "Quick-release the pressure and let the jar cool slightly.",
    "Add sliced zucchini and cook for an additional 2 minutes.",
    "Transfer the contents to a bowl and garnish with green onion, chopped cilantro, and a pinch of Korean chili flakes.",
    "Serve immediately."
